data.description: This home as it all 4-5 Bedrooms with a small office and guest quarters with its on kitchen, on two lots. The home is constructed of cinder block for durability and the roof was replaced just recently. The home features a gated fence for privacy and a large lot where you an add a mobile home or expand. The kitchen is very spacious with custom cabinetry and island, that opens to a large dining room ideal for entertaining. The downstairs room can be used as a secondary master, game room or extra living space. The upstairs guest quarters can be rented out for extra income or privacy for your guest. This home has a lot to offer call us for an appt today.
